    "While we agree that making such distinctions can be sensible, we also think that they should be grounded in a conceptually richer 2 Some literature discussed in this section predates the label 'Generative AI' (instead referring to AI) and/or deals with what defines an 'artist' or 'author', rather than a 'creator'.",
